  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Phase II Study to evaluate the response on two blocks of topotecan and carboplatin
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Phase II study for patients with chemosensible soft tissue sarcoma stage IV in children and
      adolescents ; response according to RECIST criteria following two blocks of combination
      therapy consisting of Topotecan and carboplatin
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
